# Developer Landing Backend — example requests
# Use with VS Code "REST Client" or JetBrains HTTP Client.
# Change @baseUrl to your deployment when testing the live API.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Aggregated metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metrics

### Submit a contact (valid) — full cycle: validation → rate-limit → AI → email → response
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Малик Юлдашев",
  "email": "malik@example.com",
  "phone": "+998 90 123 45 67",
  "comment": "Здравствуйте! Хотим обсудить разработку backend-сервиса с AI-интеграцией."
}

### Submit a contact (validation error — bad email & short comment → 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "A",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "phone": "abc",
  "comment": "hi"
}

### Swagger UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs

### OpenAPI schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json
